fields.name: Napa Quick Visual Inspection
fields.description: For post-transit visual inspections that may not use the standard apparatus or process
Corrosion or voids of the bussbar or other active layers of the cell or circuitry
Bent or misaligned external surfaces, including superstrates, substrates, frames and junction boxes to the extent that the installation and/or operation of the module would be impaired

fields.short_name: Cell crack removing more than 10% of cell from circuit
fields.description: Cracked or broken cells which can remove more than 10% of the cell from the electrical circuit

fields.short_name: Delamination from cell circuit to module edge
fields.description: Bubbles or delaminations forming a continuous path between any part of the electrical circuit (cell) and the edge of the module
Loss of mechanical integrity, to the extent that the installation and/or operation of the module would be impaired
Cracked or broken cells (any amount) which remove less than 10% of the cell from the circuit
Scratches; add "Comments" on the location and cause if known
Broken or faulty interconnections, joints, or terminals
Bubbles or delaminations not extending from cells to frame
Faulty terminations, exposed live electrical parts
Other - Any non-major visual defect not listed

fields.short_name: Broken, cracked, or torn external surfaces
fields.description: Broken, cracked, or torn surfaces including glass, substrate, frames, junction boxes, etc
Delamination greater than 1% of module area, if mechanical integrity depends on lamination or other means of adhesion

fields.short_name: Molten or burned areas or components
fields.description: Evidence of any molten or burned encapsulant, backsheet, frontsheet, diode, or active PV component
Missing or illegible manufacturer labels or nameplate
Loose / easily removable junction box cover
Other (major) - Any other major defect which may affect performance, safety, or function
Yellowing of backsheet, encapsulants, junction box sealant, frame sealant
Bussbar discoloration that is not corrosion
Nameplate bubbles - partial delamination of manufacturer label
Frame scratches deep enough to feel
Frame discoloration that is not corrosion
